                    'birthday' => '1979-10-08',
                    'deceased' => NULL,
                    'imdb_id' => 'nm0518085',
                    'image' => 'Kristanna_Loken_1453935473.jpg',
                    'bio' => 'Kristanna Sommer Loken was born in Ghent, New York, to Rande (Porath) and Merlin &quot;Chris&quot; Loken. She is of half Norwegian and half German descent. She began her modeling career at the early age of 15. Encouraged by her mother, who was a model prior to her daughter&#039;s birth, Kristanna&#039;s modeling career, as well as her aspirations in acting brought her to New York where she now resides. The glamorous actress/ model seems to have stayed true to her roots: her father owns an apple farm in upstate New York where he writes novels and screenplays. Aside from establishing herself as a supermodel with an Elite contract, Kristanna has made numerous television appearances as well as what could be her breakthrough film role in Terminator 3: Rise of the Machines (2003) opposite Arnold Schwarzenegger, released in 2003.',
